<section class="hero">
  <p class="eyebrow">Open source · MIT · Node 20+</p>
  <h1>Your AI coding agents' rules aren't enforced. Structor generates the validators that fail your build when they drift.</h1>
  <p class="subhead">Structor is a local CLI that generates a repository-local AI engineering harness — versioned policy, contracts, and context routing for Codex and Claude Code, with mechanical checks that catch drift before it becomes review noise.</p>
  <p class="boundary-note">A generator, not a runtime. No agents run, no sessions polled, no telemetry, no network calls during init or generate.</p>
  <div class="actions">
    <a href="https://github.com/nicolaycamacho/structor" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">View on GitHub</a>
    <a href="#demo" class="btn btn-secondary">Watch the demo</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4.5vw, 2.75rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.18;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text-strong);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 22ch;
  }

  .subhead {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.125rem);
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--text-body);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    max-width: 62ch;
  }

  .boundary-note {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2.25rem;
    max-width: 58ch;
  }

  .actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.875rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.65rem 1.35rem;
    border-radius: 5px;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    opacity: 0.88;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(29, 78, 216, 0.3);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--accent);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--accent);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--accent-subtle);
  }
</style>
